{"tid":1744892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"證券業協會：業界現結業潮　經營環境前所未有艱難","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T03:56:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"caaf163b072f17cb49af4281318b00f91c541879","tid":1744892,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493824-20191122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493824-20191122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=2ff6524c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493824-20191122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=94e300a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493824-20191122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1493824_1_L_20191122105251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1493824_1_L_20191122105251.jpg&h=5fbcec98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港證券業協會主席徐聯安表示，受社會事件影響，第2及第3季股市交投量持續低迷，按年下跌19%，而去年共有16間證券行自願暫停營業或停止營業，但今年數字截止周一增至27間，顯示業界已出現結業潮，經營環境前所未有艱難。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，10月推出的孖展新例，會令部分證券行生意受到影響。徐聯安期望，政府減免證券行持牌牌照費用，以及個人牌照費用，協助中小型證券行，長遠亦期望政府進一步幫助業界降低經營成本，例如交易所系統費用。<br />\n<br />\n提到阿里巴巴第二次來港上市，徐聯安認為，雖然香港市場持續吸引科網巨頭，但由於阿里巴巴第二次上市只有2.5%股份在港發售，相信只能提供輕微提振作用。對於近日有股份大瀉90%或以上後停牌，徐聯安認為，投資者要量力而為，同時亦需要了解清楚公司經營情況和質素。<br />\n<br />\n市傳港交所考慮洽購西班牙證券交易所，徐聯安表示，即使西班牙交易所規模相對小，但戰略意義在於增強不同地方市場網絡，以及讓其他投資者認識中國和香港的股票，增加知名度。"},{"pid":"dce6f9129b1b53ea311d9b23ae5fdf85ffbb4f1a","tid":1744892,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"咁好笑容即係無事啦"},{"pid":"feead286f60e8fd38d8c031df31d1da747e63316","tid":1744892,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"做晒大龍鳳又破壞晒規舉黎掩護中資來港上市 而家分分鐘得失晒全世界 香港班垃圾敗家官員真係好好野"},{"pid":"87d23d54e5eb08dedfa43eff18d93cc3a05eeb1e","tid":1744892,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce6f9129b1b53ea311d9b23ae5fdf85ffbb4f1a","tid":1744892,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"咁好笑容即係無事啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d5c266a7ea1186c01bfbd49c0b5af16399e732","tid":1744892,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"第二季關社會事件撚事咩"},{"pid":"c9032a42ba02e03fcc034eb4391224c0f36537fb","tid":1744892,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"但啲樓價無跌喎，係咪應該檢討下自己呢"},{"pid":"9bbe7054f8883138b9fb6ea76c0a2d1387024617","tid":1744892,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feead286f60e8fd38d8c031df31d1da747e63316","tid":1744892,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"做晒大龍鳳又破壞晒規舉黎掩護中資來港上市 而家分分鐘得失晒全世界 香港班垃圾敗家官員真係好好野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"咪係 破壞規距邊個受你玩 同支那豬一齊去鬼國玩啦"},{"pid":"7cefb931c62731c86f4bd0b82b7eeb1a0799c212","tid":1744892,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"最衰都係政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/po